      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAFFERTY BLUES (2) has been in sparkling form scoring back to back wins, the latest by 4 lengths (19.72) over 342m at this track. In form and can go on with it. CRYING TIGER (7) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 4 lengths into second (19.98) at this track in a Special conditions race over 342m. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Expected to feature again. CHARLIE'S HARLEY (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.84 beating WAIT AND SEE. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Likely to be in the finish. ASTON VERONA (4) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
